    public abstract class TransactionalEntity<I,S extends com.google.protobuf.Message,B extends io.spine.validate.ValidatingBuilder<S,? extends com.google.protobuf.Message.Builder>>
extends AbstractVersionableEntity<I,S>
    A base for entities, perform transactions events.

    Defines a transaction-based mechanism for state, version and lifecycle flags update.

    Exposes TransactionalEntity.getBuilder() validating builder} for the state as the only way to modify the state from the descendants.
